<div class="imageleft">
<img src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/McLean-b.jpg" alt width height border="1" />
<br/>
<div class="phototagleft">
</div>
</div>
<p style="margin-bottom:16px; text-indent:0in">From San Jose, <strong>Connor Lee McLean</strong> has creative nonfiction published in <em>Catamaran</em> and fiction published in <em>3:AM Magazine</em>.</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
